\"color: red;\">初步急救</span>後再送博愛醫院搶救，惜最後傷重身亡。警方在場調查，地上遺下一隻相信屬於死者的黑色皮鞋，同時在其身上檢獲一張身份證。親友其後隨警員到醫院了解。</blockquote><br />\n38樓重可以點救？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聽十字車朋友講過係例行動作<br />\n除非好明顯係死左</blockquote><br />\n除非無生命跡象<br />\n唔係救護員都要試下急救"},{"pid":"030e34225be744cc999c4d2eaefb083bc7a05626","tid":42134,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T16:17:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁早死福氣到極點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n妹妹安心上路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港早死係福氣來架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n見證唔到689下台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70fa91872c1cdc7c91b78a254eb77dd8b2cc7903","tid":42134,"uid":22360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T16:19:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁早死福氣到極點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n妹妹安心上路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港早死係福氣來架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n見證唔到689下台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n見證唔到葉劉上台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.